    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver at a lower price point. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows visible signs of its age, including some minor exterior scratches and noticeable wear on the interior upholstery. It has been maintained regularly, but potential buyers should expect some upcoming minor repairs and cosmetic touch-ups to bring it back to its best. Overall, it's a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
      "price": 21000.0,
